  <brief_title>Study to Assess Dasatinib in Patients With Core Binding Factors Acute Myelogenous Leukemia</brief_title>
  <acronym>DasaCBF</acronym>
  <official_title>An Open-Label, Multicenter, Phase II Study to Assess Dasatinib in Patients With Core Binding Factors Acute Myelogenous Leukemia Refractory to Conventional Chemotherapy or in Molecular Relapse. Intergroupe Français Des leucémie aiguë myéloblastique</official_title>
